        <p>
          UtilityHub provides web-based utilities that operate entirely within your browser. All processing is done locally, and we do not store or transmit your data.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">3. User Responsibilities</h2>
        <p>
          Users are responsible for any data they process using our tools. We recommend backing up important data before using our services.
        </p>
      </section>

